                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/15543.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Agent <persName type="from">Silliman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vera Cruz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-07-26T12:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 26, 1915—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Foreign Secretary informed me this morning that Naco had been evacuated by
                    the military after establishing civil authorities; said he was not informed as
                    to the movement on Nogales.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Silliman.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
